data.title: NWA Live Events — National Wrestling Alliance
data.meta_description: Purchase tickets to upcoming National Wrestling Alliance live events, including NWA Paranoia, CCWxNWA Viva Revolution and Tampa NWA Powerrr TV Tapings Jan. 13-14, 2024, in Ft. Lauderdale and Tampa, FL.
data.text:
NWA 76

August 31, 2024

Philadelphia, PA (2300 Arena)

It’s more than just a rumor! The National Wrestling Alliance is proud to bring NWA 76 to Philadelphia’s legendary 2300 Arena on August 31, 2024.

NWA 76 returns the NWA to the iconic professional wrestling venue for the first time in more than three decades. With all NWA titles on the line, the annual anniversary celebration is always the biggest NWA Signature Live Event of the year.

Celebrate 76 years of the National Wrestling Alliance and witness history in the making live as the company returns to Philadelphia’s most legendary pro wrestling venue.

NWA Powerrr TV Tapings

Oct. 5-6, 2024

Tampa, FL (WEDU TV Studios)

The National Wrestling Alliance returns to Tampa, FL, on Sat.-Sun., October 5-6, to film another exciting season of flagship weekly broadcast NWA Powerrr!

Bring the entire family to witness thrilling matches, jaw dropping pro wrestling action and unforgettable moments up-close and in person at WEDU Studios in Tampa FL. Get your tickets now to experience the excitement first hand! Don’t miss out on this action-packed wrestling television taping event guaranteed to keep you on the edge of your seat.

The National Wrestling Alliance: where history lives, and legends are forged!!

Day 1: Sun., Oct. 5 TV Taping

NWA Samhain 2

NWA Signature Live Event & TV Taping

Sarasota, FL (Robarts Arena)

October 26, 2024

The National Wrestling Alliance returns to Sarasota on Oct. 26, 2024! Samhain 2 promises a spooktacular night of pro wrestling action at Florida’s famed Robarts Arena, home of the Halloween-themed spectacle’s headline-grabbing 2023 debut.

The fever dream of resident garish ghoul and pro wrestling legend “The Sinister Minister” James Mitchell, Samhain instantly became one of the most talked about NWA Signature Live Events in modern history. It’s successor should offer nothing less!

Tickets are available now for this not-to-be-missed night of pro wrestling history. Front Row, ringside seating is only $39.95. Second row seats are $34.95, and floor seating is available for $29.95.

This is fans’ opportunity to be part of a live television taping! Samhain 2 will be filmed for later broadcast on NWA Powerrr, the NWA flagship series available each Tuesday through the NWA broadcast partnership with The CW.

Tickets are on sale now for Samhain 2. Buy today!
